'''Condor''' was a [[Gender/Legends|male]] [[Gunner/Legends|gunner]] in the [[24th Bombardment Squadron]], who flew with an unnamed [[Pilot/Legends|pilot]] under the callsign [[Red Three/Legends|Red Three]] during [[Operation Hammerblow]] and the [[Battle of Doornik-319|Blockade of Doornik-319]]. He refused to attack the [[Yevetha]] once they started transmitting the recordings of hostages, and he faced the possibility of a court martial due to his actions.

